{"tid":435290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國籍女司機發火　入後波撞泰國交通警被捕","createTime":"2017-10-14T06:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T10:25:04.000Z","uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"beb83eaa9139c050a604de8416575ce72547a566","tid":435290,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"據泰國媒體報道，泰國巴堤雅發生一宗倒車撞飛交通警事件，涉及一名36歲中國籍女司機。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生於10月10日，有網民上載片段，見到有人駕駛一輛紅色私家車，未關車門就突然入後波連撞向交通警兩次，之後又再加速向前，撞到前面的電單車。<br />\n<br />\n據《星暹日報》報道，該名33歲志願交通警隨後報案，經過審訊員公佈之後，事件中駕駛紅色私家車的司機為36歲中國籍女子，譯名為Ghen Xu ，警方初步以「非安全操作駕駛致使他人受傷」罪，起訴該名司機。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的交通警表示，自己當時並非無端上前刁難，只是該名司機將車停在路中央禁止停放區域，影響交通，當時以勸阻提醒為主，沒想到車中女司機突然就發火。交通警稱「自己沒有受傷，就是被彈開了」，至於肋骨骨折的電單車司機，目前正在當地醫院留醫。"},{"pid":"986ca9cae884edaa6d891270718767d9059a7b7e","tid":435290,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:03:17.000Z","msg":"屌，ban撚咗佢，唔俾咁入境"},{"pid":"ce8965018f76ea7e3f275051b5e241e84eabc8b4","tid":435290,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"泰國個監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4783f247ad9afa691921b23eb750f08f6c5fcf","tid":435290,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，ban撚咗佢，唔俾咁入境</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔好<br />\n係秦國坐陣監先再掟佢出去, 以為唔俾佢入境啦"},{"pid":"af5710e20cfd06d6d915fcb063480ad1351dbd1a","tid":435290,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbeeb8f0079bbdb78b559dbe3774adf9c1d5dc2","tid":435290,"uid":131033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"睇左&lsquo;波&rsquo;撞秦國交通警被捕"},{"pid":"7f712a6348a7efc99b92d3c5a01fba8bb614edc6","tid":435290,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:03:32.000Z","msg":"泰國d降頭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15b158932e37608b00867c0292ed08d76fb77d3","tid":435290,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"槍斃個支那女人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59900870ec8260f05b4a2ecbc47ef47f4557f113","tid":435290,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泰國個監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內臟供應商"}]}